        "TileImage": "$($repository 6a3ae9cb-1a19-4748-8450-6d241eb46e6b).Image",
        "Description": "Hush&apos;s Bodyguard, The Mogwai, has been offered millions of dollars by a technology competitor of Hush&apos;s corporation. In exchange, The Mogwai has planned to meet up with an undercover informant of the company, Buck McKeever. Take both of them out without alerting anyone so that both companies&apos; trails fall off. We recommend embedding yourself within the street guards to get close to them.",
